		biletele un string in javascript pe care il pun dupa in value
		-->
		<input class='ascuns' type='text' name='nrLoc'>
		<input class='ascuns' type='text' name='nrBilete'> <!--adulti,copii, split in node si decrementez-->
		<input class='ascuns' type='text' name='numeClient'>
		<input id="but" type="submit" value='Next' formaction="last">
		</form>
	</main>

</body>
